message.content:
1. Patients were assigned to a text messaging adjunct.
2. Patients were also assigned to a control condition.
3. Patients in the text messaging adjunct generally attended more sessions.
4. The median number of sessions attended by patients in the text messaging adjunct was 6.
5. The median number of sessions attended by patients in the control condition was 2.5.
6. The difference in session attendance between the two groups was not statistically significant.
7. The Wilcoxon-Mann-Whitney z score for the difference was -1.65.
8. The P value for the difference was .10.
